&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Director will facilitate the representation of clients in the buying and selling of commercial properties, providing essential support in negotiations between buyers and sellers. This role involves acting as an intermediary to ensure successful transactions and optimal outcomes for all parties involved.&lt;/p&gt;
